ered in this work turn out to have the\nhigh-lying GT excited states beyond one nucleon threshold, which are shown to\nbe consistent with available experimental data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 May 2012 11:20:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Dec 2012 01:54:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 28 May 2013 03:01:19 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 6 Sep 2014 07:31:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-09"}
