correlations cannot be perfect, that the wave function should not be\ntreated as an attribute of the individual quantum system which can be change\ninstantaneously and that the unperformed experiments have no results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 May 2012 15:21:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Jun 2012 15:20:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 8 Jun 2021 15:56:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-09"}
